      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:43:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>微软 Azure 增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/microsoft-s-azure-growth-slows-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软的 Azure 云计算服务季度增长放缓，这对急切希望看到对人工智能产品的巨额投资获得回报的投资者的耐心构成了考验。瑞穗美洲全球股票董事总经理 Daniel O&#39;Regan 与 Ed Ludlow 一起参加“彭博科技”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/microsoft-s-azure-growth-slows-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 20:41:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
